review_blob: This beer here is no double dutch bus. But 6 will eh-nialate you. It is quite delicious on a hot summer day. Drink Me!
Try my hand at a galctic cat and a street wizard break dance competition. I vote for Brown abbey beer because its got moves.
This is a heavy brown ale. And definitely has a nutty aroma and taste. When hitting the slopes in the rockies, this beer will warm you up with a bear hug thatll keep you coming back for more!
